alphabetsoup.waypointgraph
Class WaypointGraph

java.lang.Object
  alphabetsoup.waypointgraph.WaypointGraph

public class WaypointGraph
extends java.lang.Object

WaypointGraph maintains a collection of connected Waypoints, and the associated ways to reference and manage them.

Author:
Chris Hazard
